        name: 'Tzolk\'in (260-Day Cycle)',
        frcMapping: 'Pattern recurrence period',
        description: 'The 260-day sacred calendar (13 × 20) creates a rhythm of archetypal energies. Our system recognizes similar cyclical patterns in dimensional activation.',
